{"tid":451843,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 無料無痛 V2ray 翻牆設定教學 - Window 篇","createTime":"2017-10-29T15:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T16:27:45.000Z","uid":4055,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61ec80cd6e70c262549d0546327c7119e58663a1","tid":451843,"uid":4055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"其實連登勁多高手，可能呢篇教學對你地嚟講太簡單喇。<br />\n之前一篇 VPS 教學，一篇華碩 router 教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/438769/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/438769/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/449883/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/449883/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過對於唔係時常上大陸嘅人說服佢租部 VPS 就真係太難喇<br />\n而華碩 router 亦唔係人人有，亦無理由因為咁而換router<br />\n所以今次就出篇幾乎人人都有嘅 Window 篇<br />\n基本上係上大陸嘅時候長開屋企部電腦就 OK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enterpr1se.info/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/v2ray-over-gfw-windows-600x320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enterpr1se.info%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fv2ray-over-gfw-windows-600x320.jpg&h=24102fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次用 Winodws 10 示範，其他 Winodws 應該都差唔多；<br />\n設定基本上無難度，最難部份係響 router 做 port forward，同埋最好將部 winodw 機 fix ip<br />\n之後應該就 ok 喇<br />\n<br />\n因為寫咗兩篇，所以 iOS / Android 等教學就麻煩睇返之前果兩篇文喇<br />\n希望大家都用到無問題喇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enterpr1se.info/2017/10/v2ray-over-gfw-windows-server-edition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enterpr1se.info%2F2017%2F10%2Fv2ray-over-gfw-windows-server-edition%2F&d=SQ%2BULagOSE9CmQE7HuI2KJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=01d0268a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.enterpr1se.info/2017/10/v2ray-over-gfw-windows-server-edition/</a><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話大家 like 呢個 page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/enterpr1se.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fenterpr1se.info%2F&d=SQ%2BULagOSE9CmQE7HuI2KJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6210c06b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/enterpr1se.info/</a><br />\n同埋 share 呢個 post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/enterpr1se.info/posts/1823333511028596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fenterpr1se.info%2Fposts%2F1823333511028596&d=SQ%2BULagOSE9CmQE7HuI2KJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c55b05f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/enterpr1se.info/posts/1823333511028596</a><br />\n感激不盡"},{"pid":"0d30010643fb0d791741a63026e23e2d1990ff0e","tid":451843,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"Trashdow 不了"}]}